data.description: Your new home awaits in Quail Creek, nestled within highly desirable Stonebridge Ranch community right in the heart of McKinney. This single-story gem boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and just over 2,300 sqft of living space, offering room to grow and thrive. Inside find 2 spacious living rooms, formal dining converted to office, & modern updates throughout. The neutral color palette provides a blank canvas for your personal touch. Chef's kitchen boasts abundance of cabinetry & counter space, electric cooktop, stainless steel appliances, & overlooks cozy family room w fireplace. Step into the backyard to find your private oasis: serene koi pond and inviting in-ground pool beckon you to relax and unwind. The generously sized, partially covered patio is ideal for gatherings and outdoor entertainment. Walking distance of Stonebridge Ranch's Beach Club, ensuring endless opportunities for fun and community. McKinney ISD! Meticulously maintained & move in ready for you & your family!
